parameters: Villager C: "With this, we might be able to win"
Villager D: "Mr. Kru! Hang in there!"
Kru: "Haa haa haa... It's getting pretty tough..."
Villager B: "Kru-san... You must be in a lot of pain..."
Kru: "I-I'm fine! I can still go on!"

Kru: (Damn... The damage is bigger than I thought... And my sword skill has
expired... But just a little more...)
Villager A: "Kru-san... You seem to be in a lot of pain..."

Villager B: "Ah... It was indeed impossible to take on that many people
alone..."

Kru: "Could it be... the Golem unit... to think they were already
complete..."
Villager A: "What the hell is that thing..."
Villager B: "Something like that... we can't possibly be its enemy..."
Villager C: "This is the end for sure!"
Kru: "Damn it! I won't let them lay a hand on everyone in the village!"
Villager B: "Waaah... it's coming this way..."
Villager A: "Kru-san! You're still standing with that body of yours..."

Villager B: "Kru-san... it's enough... it's okay now... with your body all
battered like that..."

Villager G: "Ah... Umi-chan must truly be a child of God sent by Lady
Kusechirei..."
Umi: "Kru... You've done well to fight until you're so battered."
Kru: "Ah... my wounds... Umi... thank you."
Umi: "But... Kru! With this, we can!"
Kru: "Umi... I can do it... I can go on!"
Umi: "Kru! Win! Win with that power... and come back to everyone!"
Kru: "Ah! With this power, I can!"
Villager A: "Incredible... That strong-looking golem has been..."
Kru: "Umi! Thank you! You're so powerful!"
Umi: "Mmm... It's your strength, Kru... Thank you..."
Kru: "No, it's too early to be thanking me..."
Kru: "We must defeat the root of all evil!"
